            "descriptionRaw": "<color=#FFD780FF>Normal Attack</color>\nPerforms up to 4 lightning attacks that deal <color=#FFACFFFF>Electro DMG</color>.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Charged Attack</color>\nConsumes a certain amount of Stamina to deal <color=#FFACFFFF>AoE Electro DMG</color> after a short casting time.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Plunging Attack</color>\nGathering the might of Electro, Lisa plunges towards the ground from mid-air, damaging all opponents in her path. Deals <color=#FFACFFFF>AoE Electro DMG</color> upon impact with the ground.",
            "name": "Lightning Touch"
        },
